</section>


<section class="bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900/30 w-full" style="padding-top: 50px; padding-bottom: 50px;">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center"> 
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-100">See what's possible in 2 minutes</h2>
    
    <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Take a quick tour of how Diversdesk streamlines your bookings and inventory management.
    </p>

    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border-4 border-white dark:border-neutral-800" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <iframe 
            class="aspect-video w-full" 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/d7PkDQr4Dpw" 
            title="Diversdesk Intro" 
            frameborder="0" 
            allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-center" style="padding-top: 50px; padding-bottom: 50px;">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-100">
      Maximize Your Experience
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Diversdesk is powerful and flexible. To help you get the absolute most out of your trial, we recommend a 15-minute jumpstart call with our team.
    </p>

